# These notes were used to construct the regexps used for
# conditional compilation directive categorization --gjb

o #if vs. #ifdef/#ifndef
o of #if-s, are arguments expressions or just single defined(foo)/!defined(foo)?
o Histogram of # of cases
   #if ... #endif has 1
   #if #else #endif has 2
   #if #elif #endif has 2.5 or 3
   #if #elsif #else #endif has 3
  etc.
o How deeply are #if-s nested
  (can we ignore multiple-inclusion prevention from this?)
o Rough intent of purpose (see below categories and examples)
o Bodies (enclosed "scope")
   * No. of lines
   * CPP only, C only, Both


